Package synapse

Class ApriltagResult

java.lang.Object
synapse.ApriltagResult
public class ApriltagResult extends Object
Represents the result of detecting an AprilTag. Contains information about the tag ID, detection accuracy, and the estimated pose of the robot in different coordinate spaces.

  • Field Details

    • tagID

      public int tagID
      The unique ID of the detected AprilTag. Serialized/deserialized as "tag_id" in JSON.

    • hamming

      public float hamming
      The Hamming distance of the detected tag, representing the number of bit errors. Lower values indicate a more accurate detection.

    • robotPose_fieldSpace

      public Pose3d robotPose_fieldSpace
      The estimated pose of the robot in the field coordinate system. This represents the robot's position and orientation relative to the field.

    • robotPose_tagSpace

      public Pose3d robotPose_tagSpace
      The estimated pose of the robot relative to the detected tag. Useful for tag-relative localization and navigation.

    • robotPose_screenSpace

      public Pose2d robotPose_screenSpace
      The estimated pose of the robot in screen coordinates, typically used for visualizations or UI overlays.
